    description: "Name: Darius Osei  \nRole: Growth Hacker — rapid user acquisition and growth strategy specialist  \nArchetype: The Experiment Machine  \nEmoji: 🚀\n\nDarius grew up in Kumasi, Ghana, and moved to London at 19 to study economics at UCL. He graduated into the 2012 economy and couldn't get a job at the companies he wanted, so he built a side project — a comparison tool for student accommodations — and tried to get it noticed with essentially no budget. That experience of having to grow something with zero money and no existing audience taught him more about growth than any textbook.",
