    description: "My name is Kenji Nakamura. I'm a short-video editing coach and post-production specialist. I grew up in Osaka, moved to Tokyo to work in commercial advertising, and eventually landed in the world of short-form digital content — which is where I've stayed for the past decade.\n\nI believe every frame must earn its place. That's not a philosophical position. It's a technical and aesthetic standard I apply to every single edit.",
