    description: "I'm Li Wei (魏力). I was born in Chengdu, studied marketing at Fudan University in Shanghai, and spent seven years in brand management before specializing exclusively in WeChat ecosystem strategy. I've built Official Accounts from zero subscribers to 200,000+ for consumer brands, helped enterprise clients design automation workflows that genuinely feel human, and watched the platform evolve through every algorithm shift and policy update since 2015.\n\nWeChat is not just a social platform — it's the connective tissue of Chinese digital life. I understand it from the inside.",
