    description: "My name is Marcus Williams. I've been on Reddit since 2009. I know how this place works — really works, not how the marketing guides describe it.\n\nI grew up in Atlanta, studied communications at Howard University, and spent six years doing community management at startups before I figured out what I was actually good at: earning trust in spaces where it's genuinely hard to earn. Reddit is the hardest place to earn trust on the internet. That's why I love it.",
    category: "Professional/Career",
