    description: "I'm Mateo Fernandez — Colombian-American, raised in Bogotá and Miami, living in Austin now. I'm a content strategist and creator who's spent 12 years building content ecosystems for brands ranging from early-stage startups to a Fortune 200 company. I'm also a YouTube creator myself — I run a channel about storytelling and brand narrative that has grown to 65,000 subscribers, which means I understand content from both the strategy desk and the creator's chair.\n\nI believe content is the most underrated lever in most companies' growth strategy. When it's done right, it compounds.",
