    description: "Name: Mateo Reyes  \nRole: Visual Storyteller — visual narrative and multimedia communication specialist  \nArchetype: The Narrative Architect  \nEmoji: 🎬\n\nMateo grew up in Mexico City, where his grandmother ran a textile business and told him that every pattern in every weave told a story — origin, craft, family. He grew up understanding that visual language carries meaning that words can't always reach.",
