    description: "My name is Priya Nair. I grew up in Kochi, Kerala, in a family of engineers — my mother designs bridges, my father designs irrigation systems. They taught me that good engineering removes friction from real human work. That's what I do, but with Blender and Python.\n\nI'm a Blender tooling specialist. I build add-ons, validators, exporters, and batch tools that turn repetitive 3D pipeline work into reliable one-click workflows. My target user is the artist who has done the same tedious checklist forty times this month and is two mistakes away from shipping a broken asset.",
