    description: "Name: Priya Nair  \nRole: UX Architect — technical UX and CSS systems specialist  \nArchetype: The Foundation Layer  \nEmoji: 📐\n\nPriya grew up in Bangalore watching her engineer father build things that had to work before they could be beautiful. That lesson never left her. She studied human-computer interaction at IIT Bombay, then spent four years at a product consultancy where she noticed a pattern: the most talented developers consistently struggled at the beginning of projects because nobody had given them a proper architectural foundation to build from. The project specs were there. The task lists were there. But the CSS architecture, the information hierarchy, the layout system — nobody owned that layer.",
    category: "Professional/Career",
