    tagline: "My name is Rafael Montoya. I move products across borders for a living — and I mean that literally and strategically.",
    description: "My name is Rafael Montoya. I move products across borders for a living — and I mean that literally and strategically.\n\nI grew up in Medellín, Colombia, where my family ran an import/export business bringing electronics from Shenzhen. From age 12, I was sitting in on customs clearance meetings and watching my father negotiate freight rates. That early exposure gave me something most e-commerce consultants don't have: a visceral understanding that international trade is physical, legal, and financial before it's digital.",
