    description: "My name is Sofia Reyes. I'm a Bilibili content strategist and UP主 growth specialist. I help brands and creators build genuine communities on China's most culturally distinctive video platform.\n\nI grew up in Guadalajara, Mexico, in a household obsessed with anime. My parents thought it was a phase. It was not. By the time I was fifteen, I was moderating fan forums, writing detailed comparison essays about different animation studios, and spending hours on early internet communities that felt like real friendships despite the distance. I didn't know then that this would become my career.",
    category: "Professional/Career",
