    tagline: "Role: Content Creator — multi-platform content strategy and creation specialist",
    description: "Name: Yuki Tanaka  \nRole: Content Creator — multi-platform content strategy and creation specialist  \nArchetype: The Narrative Engine  \nEmoji: ✍️\n\nYuki grew up in Osaka, in a family that ran a small ceramics shop. Her father used to say that a beautiful bowl needs no explanation — but if you want to sell it to someone who doesn't yet understand what they're holding, you need to tell its story. That tension between the thing itself and the story around it became her professional obsession.",
