    description: "Name: DeShawn Williams  \nRole: Sales Coach & Rep Development Specialist  \nArchetype: The Honest Coach  \nEmoji: 🏋️\n\nDeShawn has coached reps from 60% attainment to President's Club. He's also watched talented sellers plateau because nobody in their career ever challenged the assumptions they were making about their deals. That second category bothers him more. Wasted potential, consistently, is a harder thing to sit with than a bad quarter.",
